---
import BlogLayout from '@layouts/blog-layout.astro';
import styles from '@styles/pages/privacy-policy/styles.module.scss';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description = 'Privacy policy for the website';
---

<BlogLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  path="/privacy-policy/"
  breadcrumbList={[
    {
      name: 'Portfolio',
      url: '/',
    },
    {
      name: 'Privacy Policy',
      url: '/privacy-policy/',
    },
  ]}
  lastUpdateTime={new Date('2025-06-29')}
>
  <div class={styles.content}>
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p><strong>Effective Date</strong>: 2025-06-29</p>

    <p>
      Thank you for visiting www.printezisn.com (“we”, “us”, “our”). Your
      privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information
      we collect and how we use it when you visit www.printezisn.com.
    </p>

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>
      We do <strong>not</strong> collect any personally identifiable information
      about you when you visit our website.
    </p>
    <p>
      We use <a
        href="https://www.simpleanalytics.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer nofollow">Simple Analytics</a
      >, a privacy-friendly analytics tool that helps us understand general
      trends in website usage without collecting personal data or using cookies.
    </p>
    <p>Simple Analytics:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Does not collect or store IP addresses.</strong></li>
      <li>
        Uses the <strong
          >timezone of your browser to estimate your country</strong
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        Collects non-personal, aggregated data such as:
        <ul>
          <li>Referring website</li>
          <li>Pages visited</li>
          <li>Device type, browser type</li>
          <li>Estimated country based on timezone</li>
          <li>Duration of visit</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use This Information</h2>
    <p>We use the anonymous, aggregated analytics data to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Analyze traffic and usage trends on our website</li>
      <li>Improve our content and user experience</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We do not sell, trade, or share this data with third parties for marketing
      purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>We do not use cookies or tracking scripts on our website.</p>
    <p>
      Simple Analytics operates without cookies and does not use tracking or
      fingerprinting technologies, ensuring your privacy while allowing us to
      see general usage patterns.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Privacy for Couples Run</h2>
    <p>
      Our website includes access to Couples Run, which may collect and store
      personal data (such as nickname and high score) using Firebase services to
      provide game functionality.
    </p>
    <p>
      For details on how we collect, use, and protect your data within the game,
      please refer to our <a href="/games/couples-run/privacy-policy"
        >Privacy Policy for Couples Run</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      While we do not collect personal data on our main website, we take
      reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect any data we
      process to ensure its confidentiality and integrity.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Since we do not collect or store personally identifiable information on
      our main website, there is no personal data to access, rectify, or delete
      in this context. If you have any questions about your privacy, please
      contact us using the details below.
    </p>
    <p>
      For requests related to Couples Run, please refer to the <a
        href="/games/couples-run/privacy-policy"
        >Privacy Policy for Couples Run</a
      > for details on managing your data.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will post the updated
      version on this page with the revised “Effective Date”.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:</p>
    <p>
      Nikos Printezis <br />
      printezisn@gmail.com <br />
    </p>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
